{"featured_counts":0,"common_counts":12,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":true,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560858738/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=2\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560858738/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=0\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":2},"data":[{"id":566545853,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566545853","content":"其一：在此用哲学的观点：事物都有两面性。\u003cbr\u003e其二：抛开文理：一切的标准是建立在现有知识的现有理论基础论证的认可之上的。并不代表未来。\u003cbr\u003e其三：你的观点好偏激。（个人看法，别打我）\u003cbr\u003e其四：我发表言论的主要含义：毫不在贬低标准性，而是期待。\u003cbr\u003e   ","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545919855,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"0ec085f233af039fe8a0cd0ea376e48c","url_token":"gai-gai-gai-gai-gai-2","name":"铮铮铮铮铮","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/989ab4f722c3d80c6938c563fbfccf20_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/989ab4f722c3d80c6938c563fbfccf20_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/0ec085f233af039fe8a0cd0ea376e48c","user_type":"people","headline":"俄语俄语书法小生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":7,"child_comments":[{"id":566558759,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566558759","content":"\u003cp\u003e所以您还是不懂哥猜究竟是什么程度的问题，而且我说的是，任何一个真正提出颠覆性理论的研究者，都建立在对现有知识现有理论基础的【掌握】上的，你可以不认可，但是只有掌握了现有的情况和知识，才有资格说创新，颠覆，建立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e没有掌握现有的知识和理论基础的人妄言创新，就像说自己发明了永动机一样，这样自称要想得到尊重，前提是你真正掌握了热力学四大定律（把第零定律也算进去吧）及其数理证明和实验现象，还必须掌握根据热力学基本定律发展而来的物理学界最前沿的知识（充斥着大量艰涩难懂的方程和数理知识），再说修正了热力学定律，数理过程是什么，实验结果怎么证明，公开接受同行评议。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在这样的知识掌握量下，哪怕见解是不够准确的，错的水平也不会太低，思路才有可以参考价值。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不然这不是侮辱知识，傲慢自大又是什么？用三角函数推翻相对论，用初等数论证明哥猜，用微波炉烘烤把铁变成金，这样的“创新”和“勇气”对认真学习前人知识的我等学渣算什么？对将理化知识发展到现今程度的前辈又算什么？凭什么无数聪明绝顶的前辈和芸芸众生为这个学科付出青春年华和汗水，被这样没有掌握前沿知识的人说大话，还要被您这样不清楚科学研究过程的人“期待”？\u003c/p\u003e","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545921608,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"reply_to_author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"0ec085f233af039fe8a0cd0ea376e48c","url_token":"gai-gai-gai-gai-gai-2","name":"铮铮铮铮铮","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/989ab4f722c3d80c6938c563fbfccf20_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/989ab4f722c3d80c6938c563fbfccf20_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/0ec085f233af039fe8a0cd0ea376e48c","user_type":"people","headline":"俄语俄语书法小生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0},{"id":566564818,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566564818","content":"\u003cp\u003e爱因斯坦相对论修正了牛顿的定理，爽吧，但是爱因斯坦16岁自学完微积分，21岁发表论文在学术杂志上，26岁提出光量子假说并取得博士学位，期间一直阅读并掌握了方向内的最前沿知识。爱因斯坦不提出颠覆性的观点，他也是物理领域内真正的专家，提出来了，他就是天才。这个小孩要是能做到掌握哥猜领域最前沿的数学工具和数理知识，那不管他证明得对不对，我都很期待。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果他掌握了，清北直博都完全OK，也不会问这个问题了。很明显，他没有。\u003c/p\u003e","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545922412,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"reply_to_author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"0ec085f233af039fe8a0cd0ea376e48c","url_token":"gai-gai-gai-gai-gai-2","name":"铮铮铮铮铮","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/989ab4f722c3d80c6938c563fbfccf20_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/989ab4f722c3d80c6938c563fbfccf20_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/0ec085f233af039fe8a0cd0ea376e48c","user_type":"people","headline":"俄语俄语书法小生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0}]}]}
